<br>
If I am busy and porting to a place you need to go, you will never see me refuse. Why be a greedy ass for 5mins when you can certainly get that cash back in 10mins or so.... Beats the hell out of me why a porter would really REALLY need 20-50pp for.... to run a bank? You won't need money to go to one of those.<br>
<br>
