<br>
Now if you run into a wizard who charges for a port to wherever they are going... you ran into a silly wizard =) Now if I am hunting and you ask for a port, I merely say no, if you are rude to me then I will make a note of it that when I can port you, and you are screaming across the zone, I'll ignore it and will go so far to port someone else in front of you and not you. <br>
<br>
Be polite and everyone will be your friend, and in doing so you won't have to pay for anything anymore.. <br>
<br>
