When I'm not busy:<br>
I will port people shouting for a port that give a money amount.<br>
I take half or less than half of whatever amount they offered.<br>
I'll port people that need to get their corpses and obviously have no money on them, or people below 30 that aren't totally twinked for free.<br>
On alts, I do a /who on druids and wizards in the zone and send a tell to one 'please for 20-50pp (depending on how much money the alt has) will you port me to X?' It's straight forward, to the point, and personal to them.<br>
For rezzes, I just don't die =D<br>
hehe but usually if for some odd reason I did I can wait around till someone in my super guild can do it for me.<br>
